    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Displays that transmit and reflect visible information from a computer or device to a human viewer. There are varying forms of flat-panel displays due to changes in technology or innovation, such as the liquid crystal display (LCD) or the plasma display. These displays may be found on a variety of portable computers, from televisions to digital watches. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
